dishes.name: X-space Private Room
dishes.label: Hot
dishes.description: X-space Private Room is an advanced and modern net gaming room service, specifically designed to meet the needs of professional gamers as well as groups or individuals who love video games. This service provides a private, comfortable and high-quality space for every gaming experience.

dishes.name: Normal Class
dishes.description: The basic gaming package is a gaming package that includes services such as high-configuration computers that provide experience with famous and diverse games. Gaming chair service brings gamers the same experience when playing.

dishes.name: Normal Meal
dishes.label: New
dishes.description: Basic meals with a variety of options and providing full nutrition as well as delicious taste, giving gamers full energy when playing games.

dishes.name: Special Meal
dishes.description: Offering special meals with a full range of dishes, the store offers an excellent food menu that brings an extremely good experience to customers.

promotions.name: Event Gaming
promotions.label: New
promotions.description: Often organizes events and tournaments with valuable trophies. The tournament has many players participating in many diverse forms such as team and individual matches.

leaders.name: Thầy Giáo Ba
leaders.description: Our CEO, Mr. Dad is a professional gamer and trainer of the game League of Legends (League of Legends). Teacher Ba used to be a professional gamer of League of Legends. After that, he became the coach of Team FFQ. Later, he gave up his coaching position to focus on livestreaming on his Youtube channel Ba Roi Beo.

leaders.name: Xemesis
leaders.description: Our CFO, Xemesis is a famous streamer in Saigon that is loved and followed by many young people. Besides, Xemesis is also a successful businessman and owns many internet shops, motorbike garages, etc. In particular, people often talk about Xemesis as the richest streamer with a willingness to play and spend huge amounts of money on his cars.

leaders.name: Misthy
leaders.description: MisThy is a Vietnamese female streamer, female video game gamer, female YouTuber and actress. With a pretty face and the ability to interact well with the audience every time she goes on air, Thy Ngoc is a Streamer who is always loved by the audience.

leaders.name: Viruss
leaders.description: ViruSs's real name is Dang Tien Hoang, is a multi-talented, gallant Gamer - Streamer - Caster of the Vietnamese League of Legends (LMHT) village. ViruSs is originally a professional gamer, having fought for many strong teams such as Hanoi Dragon (captain), Cyzone... ViruSs is one of the gamers with the greatest influence on the League of Legends community.
